{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 40.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually, all 1,200 of us who finally were mustered out and brought into the barrack, we all knew that we had to be mechanics.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally, one day, there was an officer of the Organisation Todt-- which was the heavy construction organization of the German state corporation-- came in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taken out one by one from the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he stood there with a proportional caliper in his hand, and I was asked to translate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as each man approached, he would ask me to ask him what his profession was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would try telling-- this man wants to know whether you are a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I turned back to him, and say, he says he's a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for the sake of variety, I would say he's a bicycle mechanic, a motorcycle mechanic, or a locksmith, or a this, or a that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so all 1,200 of us became mechanics.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's-- this is another aspect of this simplicity and almost primitivity, at least, of the whole procedure, that I could convert 1,200 people into mechanics.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you would have thought that the Germans in Hungary selected 1,200 mechanics from the whole country and brought them together and brought them to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, because we were mechanics, we were apparently, as it turned out to be later, hired out to the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we left Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's a debate between myself and my sister whether it was two weeks after we arrived or three weeks after we arrived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was taken to France, to a place which I later discovered was Longwy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the camp was outside this town called [FRENCH], which was a mining area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were to have brought a airplane fuselage factory into the mines.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
